query:
SELECT count(*)
                FROM room_member rm1
                JOIN room_member rm2 ON rm1.room_id = rm2.room_id
                JOIN room r ON rm1.room_id = r.id
                WHERE rm1.user_id = $1 AND rm2.user_id = $2
                  AND rm1.membership = 'Join' AND rm2.membership = 'Join'
                  AND r.type != 'Server'
